# 十九、kernel capability matrix 要求

请帮我建立 `docs/E5_kernel_capability_matrix.md`，至少包含：

```text
Capability | Kernel config | Runtime evidence | Required by | Status
MMC block | CONFIG_MMC / platform host driver | /dev/mmcblk0p2 / dmesg | rootfs A/B | PASS/FAIL
EXT4 | CONFIG_EXT4_FS | findmnt /, findmnt /data | rootfs/data | PASS/FAIL
UART console | serial driver + console support | kernel log on serial | logs/debug | PASS/FAIL
Watchdog | CONFIG_WATCHDOG + SoC driver | /dev/watchdog | E5 reset | PASS/FAIL
procfs | CONFIG_PROC_FS | /proc/cmdline | slot detect | PASS/FAIL
sysfs | CONFIG_SYSFS | /sys exists | device visibility | PASS/FAIL
devtmpfs | CONFIG_DEVTMPFS | /dev/mmcblk0 exists | boot device nodes | PASS/FAIL
```

每个能力都必须有 runtime evidence，不允许只写“已启用”。

